                <div class="text-center">
                    <h3>About US</h3>
                    <p> Due to the increasing frequency of human activities, some animal populations have shrunk or even become extinct. Therefore, from the perspective of human long-term physiology, health and spirit, it is urgent to protect the habitat of land animals and call for people to care for endangered land animals. Kolaroo is a website dedicated to promoting the protection and awareness of endangered species and habitats..</p>
